#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:28
msgid ""
"In this section you will find a summary of major gameplay elements to know "
"to become a successful player."
msgstr ""
"U ovom odjeljku naći ćete sažetak glavnih elemenata igre koje trebate znati "
"da biste postali uspješan igrač."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:31
msgid "More can be found on our website and other community places!"
msgstr ""
"Više informacija možete pronaći na našoj web stranici i drugim mjestima u "
"zajednici!"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:33
msgid ""
"Chat with players and developers on Libera.Chat IRC, Matrix or Discord: <web "
"dest=\"chat\" />"
msgstr ""
"Čavrljajte s igračima i programerima na Libera.Chat IRC-u, Matrixu ili "
"Discordu:<web dest=\"chat\" />"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:34
msgid "Discuss news in the forums: <web dest=\"forums\" />"
msgstr "Raspravite o novostima na forumima:<web dest=\"forums\" />"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:35
msgid "Discover more about the game in the wiki: <web dest=\"wiki\" />"
msgstr "Saznajte više o igri na wiki stranici:<web dest=\"wiki\" />"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:37
msgid "Please report bugs on: <web dest=\"bugs\" />"
msgstr "Molimo prijavite greške na:<web dest=\"bugs\" />"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:41
msgid "Income &amp; evolution"
msgstr "Prihod i evolucija"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:45
msgid ""
"Aliens can earn evolution points by killing humans. They can then use those "
"evolution points to evolve into [dragoon] more advanced forms."
msgstr ""
"Vanzemaljci mogu zaraditi evolucijske bodove ubijajući ljude. Zatim mogu "
"koristiti te evolucijske bodove da evoluiraju u [zmajske] naprednije oblike."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:48
msgid ""
"Aliens can evolve from everywhere if not in line of sight of an human player "
"or buildable. Aliens can also devolve to [granger] less advanced forms (at "
"some cost) when being near the [overmind] overmind."
msgstr ""
"Vanzemaljci se mogu razvijati odasvud, osim ako nisu u vidokrugu ljudskog "
"igrača ili izgradive građevine. Vanzemaljci se također mogu degenerirati u "
"[granger] manje napredne oblike (uz određenu cijenu) kada su u blizini "
"[overmind] nadsvjesnog uma."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:51
msgid ""
"Build an overmind with a [granger] granger if it gets destroyed, you need a "
"live overmind to evolve!"
msgstr ""
"Izgradite nadsvijest s [granger] grangerom, ako bude uništena, potreban vam "
"je živi nadsvijest da biste evoluirali!"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:55
msgid ""
"Humans can earn credits by killing aliens and destroying alien buildables, "
"then they can uses those credits to buy new [lcannon] weapons, body armours "
"or [bsuit] battlesuit, and accessories like a radar or a jetpack."
msgstr ""
"Ljudi mogu zaraditi kredite ubijanjem vanzemaljaca i uništavanjem "
"vanzemaljskih objekata, a zatim te kredite mogu koristiti za kupovinu novog "
"oružja [lcannon], pancira ili borbenog odijela [bsuit] i dodataka poput "
"radara ili jetpacka."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:58
msgid ""
"Humans buy and sell weapons at the [armoury] armoury, make sure one is "
"built! Use the construction kit to build an armoury if it's missing."
msgstr ""
"Ljudi kupuju i prodaju oružje u oružarnici [armourmy], pobrinite se da je "
"jedna izgrađena! Koristite komplet za konstrukciju da izgradite oružarnicu "
"ako nedostaje."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:62
msgid "Powering buildables"
msgstr "Napajanje gradivih elemenata"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:65
msgid ""
"Building a structure requires build points. Your team will start with a "
"small pool of build points but if you want to place a greater number of "
"buildables in an area, you can build a [leech] mining structure to increase "
"the available power and provide more build points. Be wary that you will "
"loose the build points if the mining structures are destroyed."
msgstr ""
"Izgradnja strukture zahtijeva bodove za izgradnju. Vaš tim će početi s malim "
"brojem bodova za izgradnju, ali ako želite postaviti veći broj objekata za "
"izgradnju u određenom području, možete izgraditi rudarsku strukturu "
"[pijavica] kako biste povećali dostupnu snagu i osigurali više bodova za "
"izgradnju. Budite oprezni jer ćete izgubiti bodove za izgradnju ako se "
"rudarske strukture unište."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:68
msgid ""
"When you are using more BP (Build Point) than the mining structures ([leech] "
"Leech, [drill] Drill) are capable of providing (current BPs + BPs you will "
"recover over time), buildables will power down until the other buildables "
"have enough energy to remain operational."
msgstr ""
"Kada koristite više BP (Tačaka Gradnje) nego što rudarske strukture "
"([pijavica] Pijavica, [bušilica] Bušilica) mogu da pruže (trenutne BP + BP "
"koje ćete oporaviti tokom vremena), gradive strukture će se isključiti dok "
"ostale gradive strukture ne sakupe dovoljno energije da ostanu operativne."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:69
msgid ""
"Spawn structures ([egg] eggs and [telenode] telenodes), mining structures "
"(leech and drill) and unique structures ([overmind] overmind and [reactor] "
"reactor) are NOT affected by the lack of BPs."
msgstr ""
"Nedostatak BP-ova NISU pogođene strukture za mriješćenje ([egg] jaja i "
"[telenode] telenode), strukture za rudarenje (pijavica i bušilica) i "
"jedinstvene strukture ([overmind] overmind i [reactor] reaktor)."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:73
msgid "Mining structures"
msgstr "Rudarske strukture"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:76
msgid ""
"Build points are acquired via two mining structures: the human [drill] drill "
"and the alien [leech] leech. These buildings need to be spread out for "
"efficiency."
msgstr ""
"Bodovi za izgradnju se dobijaju putem dvije rudarske strukture: ljudske "
"[bušilice] bušilice i vanzemaljske [pijavice] pijavice. Ove zgrade moraju "
"biti raštrkane radi efikasnosti."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:79
msgid ""
"Don't build mining structures too close together or they will compete with "
"each other and ultimately cost build resources!"
msgstr ""
"Nemojte graditi rudarske strukture preblizu jedna drugoj ili će se međusobno "
"takmičiti i na kraju vas koštati resursa za izgradnju!"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:82
msgid ""
"Builders will see another bar above the health bar of a resource generator "
"which represents its efficiency. A prediction will be shown when you "
"position the buildable. The build points are available instantly when the "
"mining structure finishes building, and will be subtracted back if the "
"building is destroyed. Don't build unprotected drills!"
msgstr ""
"Graditelji će vidjeti još jednu traku iznad trake zdravlja generatora "
"resursa koja predstavlja njegovu efikasnost. Predviđanje će se prikazati "
"kada pozicionirate objekat za izgradnju. Bodovi za izgradnju su odmah "
"dostupni kada se završi izgradnja rudarske strukture i bit će oduzeti ako se "
"zgrada uništi. Nemojte graditi nezaštićene bušilice!"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:85
msgid ""
"When a building is destroyed, the miners will recover its build points "
"slowly. The mine recovery rate decreases over time, so that it gets "
"increasingly harder to rebuild destroyed buildings in a long lasting match. "
"This replaces sudden death."
msgstr ""
"Kada je zgrada uništena, rudari će polako oporavljati njene bodove "
"izgradnje. Stopa oporavka rudnika se s vremenom smanjuje, tako da je sve "
"teže obnoviti uništene zgrade u dugotrajnoj utakmici. Ovo zamjenjuje "
"iznenadnu smrt."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:89
msgid "Stages &amp; Momentum"
msgstr "Faze i zamah"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:92
msgid ""
"Building and destroying structures as well as killing enemies earns your "
"team a new resource called momentum. If you gain enough momentum new "
"weapons, structures or classes will be unlocked."
msgstr ""
"Izgradnja i uništavanje struktura, kao i ubijanje neprijatelja, donosi vašem "
"timu novi resurs koji se zove momentum. Ako dobijete dovoljno momentuma, "
"otključat će se nova oružja, strukture ili klase."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:95
msgid ""
"Momentum decreases exponentially over time so if you idle your team will "
"lose access to new items. Existing upgrades will remain functional."
msgstr ""
"Momentum se eksponencijalno smanjuje tokom vremena, tako da ako mirujete, "
"vaš tim će izgubiti pristup novim predmetima. Postojeća unapređenja će "
"ostati funkcionalna."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:99
msgid "Wildfire"
msgstr "Šumski požar"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:102
msgid ""
"Alien buildables can catch fire when they are hit with the [flamer] "
"flamethrower or the [firebomb] firebomb."
msgstr ""
"Vanzemaljski gradivi objekti mogu se zapaliti kada ih pogodi bacač plamena "
"[flamer] ili zapaljiva bomba [firebomb]."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:105
msgid ""
"If structures are built too close, the fire can jump over to the unfortunate "
"neighbors."
msgstr ""
"Ako su građevine izgrađene preblizu, vatra se može proširiti na nesretne "
"susjede."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:108
msgid ""
"A small [fire] fire has a good chance to go out after a while but a group of "
"burning structures will keep itself hot enough for greater mayhem."
msgstr ""
"Mali požar ima dobre šanse da se ugasi nakon nekog vremena, ali grupa "
"zapaljenih struktura će se dovoljno zagrijati za veći haos."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:111
msgid ""
"The [advgranger] advanced granger's spit attack can be used to put out fires "
"or slow down intruders!"
msgstr ""
"Napad pljuvanjem naprednog grangera [advgranger] može se koristiti za "
"gašenje požara ili usporavanje uljeza!"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:115
msgid "Under attack"
msgstr "Pod napadom"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:118
msgid ""
"The [reactor] reactor and the [overmind] overmind will issue warnings to the "
"team when at 75% health, at 50% health, at 25% health and when destroyed."
"Destroying other buildings will trigger “under attack” warnings for the "
"owning team."
msgstr ""
"Reaktor [reactor] i nadsvjesni [overmind] će izdavati upozorenja timu kada "
"su na 75% srčane snage, na 50% srčane snage, na 25% srčane snage i kada su "
"uništeni. Uništavanje drugih zgrada će pokrenuti upozorenja \"pod napadom\" "
"za tim vlasnika."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:122
msgid "Healing"
msgstr "Iscjeljenje"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:125
msgid "Dying feeds the enemy, you may want to save your life!"
msgstr "Umiranje hrani neprijatelja, možda želiš spasiti svoj život!"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:129
msgid ""
"Aliens heal slowly wherever they are, but they heal faster in groups and "
"near alien buildables. Building forward ones can be decisive! Healing in any "
"manner will also contribute to restoring the [advdragoon] advanced dragoon "
"projectiles."
msgstr ""
"Vanzemaljci se sporo liječe gdje god se nalazili, ali brže liječe u grupama "
"i u blizini vanzemaljskih objekata za izgradnju. Izgradnja onih naprijed "
"može biti odlučujuća! Liječenje na bilo koji način će također doprinijeti "
"obnavljanju [advdragoon] naprednih zmajskih projektila."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:133
msgid ""
"The booster gives rapid healing for nearby aliens, build one as soon as you "
"can, try to unlock it the soonest possible. The booster will also gives you "
"some poison to make your attacks more deadly."
msgstr ""
"Pojačivač daje brzo iscjeljenje obližnjim vanzemaljcima, izgradite jednog "
"što prije možete, pokušajte ga otključati što je prije moguće. Pojačivač će "
"vam također dati malo otrova kako bi vaši napadi bili smrtonosniji."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:136
msgid ""
"Staying at an intermediate distance of the [overmind] overmind or [egg] eggs "
"will give you some slightly improved healing too, although lower than creep. "
"This can help defending bases."
msgstr ""
"Ostanak na srednjoj udaljenosti od [overmind] overmind ili [egg] jaja će vam "
"dati i nešto poboljšano liječenje, iako slabije nego kod creep-a. Ovo može "
"pomoći u odbrani baza."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:139
msgid ""
"Aliens have a third healing boost: proximity with other aliens. If you are "
"near a friendly fellow alien, you will heal slightly faster, and with two "
"teammates, you will heal as fast as you would by touching an alien "
"buildable. With some teamwork, this is a great way to besiege enemies!"
msgstr ""
"Vanzemaljci imaju i treće pojačanje za iscjeljenje: blizina s drugim "
"vanzemaljcima. Ako ste u blizini prijateljski nastrojenog vanzemaljca, "
"zacijelit ćete nešto brže, a s dva člana tima, zacijelit ćete brzo kao da "
"dodirujete vanzemaljsku građevinu. Uz malo timskog rada, ovo je odličan "
"način za opsadu neprijatelja!"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:143
msgid ""
"Humans carry with them a medkit they can use to heal once, after that they "
"have to return to the [medstat] medistation to heal and refill their medkit."
msgstr ""
"Ljudi sa sobom nose medicinski komplet koji mogu koristiti za jednokratno "
"liječenje, nakon čega se moraju vratiti u meditaciju [medstat] da bi se "
"izliječili i napunili svoj medicinski komplet."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:147
msgid "Wallwalking"
msgstr "Hodanje po zidovima"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:150
msgid ""
"Some alien forms like the [dretch] dretch, the [mantis] mantis and the "
"[advgranger] advanced granger can walk on walls!"
msgstr ""
"Neki vanzemaljski oblici poput [dretch] dretcha, [mantis] mantisa i "
"[advgranger] naprednog grangera mogu hodati po zidovima!"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:153
msgid "Use this to reach special places or use shortcuts through vents."
msgstr ""
"Koristite ovo da biste došli do posebnih mjesta ili koristili prečice kroz "
"ventilacijske otvore."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:156
msgid ""
"Alien defensive structures like trapper and spiker work better on walls, "
"building them on ceiling will protect them from grenades."
msgstr ""
"Vanzemaljske odbrambene strukture poput trapera i spikera bolje "
"funkcioniraju na zidovima, a njihova izgradnja na stropu zaštitit će ih od "
"granata."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:159
msgid "The advanced granger can be unlocked with momentum."
msgstr "Napredni granger se može otključati zamahom."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:163
msgid "Since Tremulous"
msgstr "Od Tremulous-a"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:166
msgid "Since Tremulous, the stamina has been increased."
msgstr "Od Tremulous-a, izdržljivost je povećana."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:169
msgid ""
"All alien evolution costs and gains have been doubled. The new maximum of "
"evos an alien can store is 20 (formerly 9)."
msgstr ""
"Svi troškovi i dobici evolucije vanzemaljaca su udvostručeni. Novi "
"maksimalni broj evoa koje vanzemaljac može pohraniti je 20 (ranije 9)."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:172
msgid ""
"Stages were replace with momentum, and build points depend directly on the "
"number of drills."
msgstr ""
"Faze su zamijenjene momentumom, a bodovi za izgradnju direktno zavise od "
"broja vježbi."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:175
msgid ""
"Humans no longer have the Tesla defense tower nor the defense computer but "
"they can build rocket pods."
msgstr ""
"Ljudi više nemaju Teslin odbrambeni toranj niti odbrambeni računar, ali mogu "
"graditi raketne kapsule."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:178
msgid ""
"Aliens got the spiker buildable that can deeply hurt imprudent humans, but "
"that's a very vulnerable structure, don't put it in plain sight!"
msgstr ""
"Vanzemaljci su uspjeli sastaviti šiljak koji može duboko povrijediti "
"nepromišljene ljude, ali to je vrlo ranjiva struktura, nemojte je stavljati "
"na vidno mjesto!"

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:181
msgid ""
"The basilisk was replaced by the mantis, it cannot grab anymore but its bite "
"slows down their victims, and it can lunge for very fast approachs."
msgstr ""
"Baziliska je zamijenila bogomoljka, više ne može hvatati, ali njen ugriz "
"usporava žrtve i može se vrlo brzo približavati."

#: ui/help_gameplay.rml:184
msgid ""
"Aliens can devolve near the overmind, and the advanced granger spit can do "
"interesting things, try it on fire or humans!"
msgstr ""
"Vanzemaljci se mogu degenerirati blizu nadsvijesti, a napredna Grangerova "
"pljuvačka može raditi zanimljive stvari, isprobati to na vatri ili ljudima!"

